show.description: Keeladi, Aathicha Nallur pondra idangalil kidaitha Pandai Kaala porutkal, Kalvettugal, Olai chuvdigal, seppedugal patri vivarangalai eduthu koorukirathu intha audio puthagam. Thamizhagathil nadantha agazh aaivugal patriya thagavalgalai vilakki koorum Audio puthagam idhu.
